  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 3e1cd92da80c7495a8fe7eb91fa80c2f, type: 3}
  m_Name: Lavender
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Plants.PlantData
  displayName: Lavender
  audioClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 5e37d7fedac5bd94fa18dd4b8d0633eb, type: 3}
  environmentPainting: {fileID: 2800000, guid: efa3e5c6db7e83d49a44ccdfcf0d6ae3, type: 3}
  poem:
    text: "Sweet Lavender\n\nIn cottage-maid's parterre thou'rt seen, \nIn simple
      touching grace ; \nAnd in the garden of the queen, \n'Midst costly plants and
      blossoms sheen, \nThou also hast a place. \nThe rose, with bright and peerless
      bloom, \nAttracted many eyes; \nBut while her glories and perfume \nExpire
      before brief summer's doom, \nThy fragrance never dies. \nBut thou art emblem
      of the friend, \nWho, whatsoe'er our lot, \nThe balm of faithful love will
      lend, \nAnd, true and constant to the end, \nMay die, but alters not.\n\n\u2014
      Agnes Strickland"
    environmentPainting: {fileID: 0}
  contextInfos:
  - text: Lavender doesn't lose its scent. Even when cut or dried, the oil holds
      for years.
    environmentPainting: {fileID: 0}
  - text: Lavender oil is also used in many aromatheraphies, especially to calm nerves,
      and in medical anxiety Treatment
    environmentPainting: {fileID: 0}
  - text: already in acient times it was know that lavender wine helpts to ease "pains
      of the side and the nerves, and extreme cold." (De Matedia medica - Dioscorides)
    environmentPainting: {fileID: 0}
  - text: the Name stems fron Latin "lavare" - washing. Romains laid it in Baths,
      beds and linen.
    environmentPainting: {fileID: 0}
  - text: To "lay up in lavender" is to fold a thing away wrapped in the herb, safe
      from moths and time.
    environmentPainting: {fileID: 0}
  - text: "Lavender - Alfred Noyes (excerpt)\nLavender, lavender, \nFrom where the
      bee hums, \nTo the loud roar of London,\nWith purple dreams he comes, \nFrom
      ragged lanes of wild-Flowers\nTo ragged London slums, \nWith a basket full
      of lavender \nAnd purple dreams he comes."
    environmentPainting: {fileID: 0}
